dc_title_s: Warren County, Iowa, 1974, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet label. Images are photoreductions of mosaics created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol 19181. Form of individual image numbering: 19181-1873-[number]. Year flown 1974. Flown by Harry S. Johnson Co. Inc. Lakeville, Minnesota.
